On [[July 7th]], [[2007]] rumors began spreading that Google would be buying out GalaxyWebs.com[http://GalaxyWebs.com] as part of a new plan to offer free [[web hosting]] services similar to those of [[Yahoo]]'s [[Geocities]]. This report has not yet been confirmed nor denied by Google.
